&h=c21a4019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前聯合國調查員傑瑞&middot;藍恩與自己的妻子凱倫和兩個女兒瑞秋與康妮，愉快的在擁擠的費城市區公路上行車，但一分鐘內就有多架直升機從空中飛過，而新聞上一直在談論關於台灣爆發的狂犬病毒。突然間，公路前方發生了爆炸，而公路上執勤的警察當場被失控的垃圾車撞死，傑瑞跟隨垃圾車的行進路線離開公路，之後與一輛失控的救護車發生相撞。傑瑞與凱倫回過神來後，帶著女兒們丟下汽車逃跑，而廣場上也轉眼間出現了幾百名瘋狂咬人的殭屍，而傑瑞與家人逃離時親眼看到一名被殭屍咬到的人，在十二秒之內也淪為了一個殭屍，後來與家人開著一輛房車逃離了城市。不到兩小時，費城淪陷，美軍阻止殭屍的軍事行動全部以失敗告終...<br />\n<br />\n1 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=504f0c01\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=e67676bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3d10725cb37b0fd665fad7d7f3b0ead9f999be","tid":2239194,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T17:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cc1fa8a9b09c3ab7cae3c8d89d6fe371829f84","tid":2239194,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}